data.description: This is the ABSOLUTE CHEAPEST price per square foot home in Rainbow Woods subdivision listed in the past 2 years, it's list price is even CHEAPER THAN ANY SOLD in the past 2 years!  4 BEDROOM 2 BATH POOL HOME ON A HALF ACRE LOT IN A QUIET CUL-DE-SAC!  Centrally located within the subdivision with a LOW yearly HOA.  Many recent upgrades including all new windows and doors (2019), NEW METAL ROOF (2018), and a new HVAC system installed in 2013 with all new ductwork PLUS a newer hot water heater.  Open floor plan with a spacious family room and vaulted ceiling, NO POPCORN.  Nice sliding glass doors that open up to the MASSIVE lanai.  Large master bedroom that's independant (opposite side of house) from the other 3 spacious bedrooms which utilize a newly renovated guest bathroom.  The kitchen is open to the family room and includes both a dinette AND breakfast bar.  The kitchen features granite counters and newer kitchen appliances.  Rainbow Woods is a small deed restricted community with a minimum 1/2 acre lot size and minimum 1600 sf home size.  With a little cosmetic elbow grease this home will be perfect to impress your family and friends!
